Package com.hms_networks.americas.sc.taginfo

Ewon Flexy tag information library created by the HMS Networks MU Americas Solution Center.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TagConstants
    Class for storing constants used in the taginfo package.
    TagGroup
    Class to represent a tag group in a similar fashion to enums in Java 1.5+.
    TagInfo
    Class to hold information about a tag and its configuration.
    TagInfoManager
    Class that allows the retrieval of tag information of an Ewon Flexy by generating an export block descriptor call and parsing the response to store as a list of TagInfo objects.
    TagType
    Class to represent tag type in a similar fashion to enums in Java 1.5+.

Package com.hms_networks.americas.sc.taginfo Description

Ewon Flexy tag information library created by the HMS Networks MU Americas Solution Center. This library is dependent on the HMS Networks MU Americas Solution Center library for strings, found at https://www.github.com/hms-networks/sc-string-lib.
Version:
1.0
Author:
HMS Networks, MU Americas Solution Center
